{
	"name": "Knight of Fire",
	"type": "feature",
	"img": "icons/magic/fire/elemental-creature-horse.webp",
	"system": {
		"description": "<p>At 5th level, your authority over fire deepens. You gain the following features:</p><ul><li><p>You can attack twice, instead of once, whenever you take the Attack action on your turn. You can replace one of these attacks with a spell whose level is not higher than your proficiency bonus. You can do this a number of times equal to your proficiency bonus per Long Rest.</p></li><li><p>You gain resistance to fire damage.</p></li><li><p>You gain one inexperienced follower. If your follower dies, after 1 month you receive word that their replacement is ready to join you.</p></li></ul>",
